# ── Embedding CSV files ───────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# merchant_embeddings.csv (1.7 MB), user_embeddings.csv (6.6 MB), and
# transaction_embeddings_slim.csv (16 MB, 1000-sample) are committed to git.
# transaction_embeddings.csv (78 MB full dataset) is excluded — over GitHub limit.
# TigerGraph stores VECTOR attributes as an internal HNSW index; they are not
# returned via REST++ — Cluster/GraphSAGE pages use these CSVs for UMAP.
data/transaction_embeddings.csv
data/vector_loads/transactions_risk_emb.csv
data/vector_loads/transactions_behavior_emb.csv
data/vector_loads/merchant_emb.csv
data/vector_loads/user_emb.csv

